How to prepare a delicious Chicken Penne

Farimah Asadi

May, 6th 2021

The Ingredients(for 2 persons):

  • \(250\) g penne
  • \(125\) g chicken meat
  • \(1\) onion
  • \(2\) garlics
  • \(20\) g butter
  • \(20\) g parsley
  • \(2\) paprika
  • \(2\) tablespoons tomato paste
  • \(2\) teaspoons of salt, pepper and turmeric
  • \(3\) tablespoons of olive oil
  • \(1\) tablespoon cream

The preparation:

Cut the onions,garlics and paprika, and fry them in olive oil. Then add the meat,tomato paste and 2 teaspoons of salt, pepper and turmic. let them slowly cook. Now you can put the penne in boiling water for 8 minutess, Then roast them in butter and cream and add the parseley. finally you can serve your penne with the wonderfull sous and some fresh vegetables.

Bon appetit!
